Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是"我要去太空漫步"的意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That was your "going on a spacewalk" face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保證不會再去太空漫步了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No more spacewalks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去休息吧  好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get some rest, ok?
