Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有女朋友了  芬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have a girlfriend, Finn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒什么可說的了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's really nothing left to say.
