Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在意雷文\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I care about Raven.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你和我  我們擦出過火花\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you and me, we started something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什么不能終止的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's nothing we can't stop.
