Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我可不確定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伙兒們  快過來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Guys, guys. Come here!
