Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾百具尸體從方舟上被送回了地球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hundreds of bodies being returned to the earth from the ark.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從地球上看來就像是流星雨一般\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is what it looks like from the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:07:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們沒收到我們的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They didn't get our message.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都怪你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is all because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你找到了無線電\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I helped you find the radio.
