Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.91,0:08:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  他清楚這一點\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, he knows.
