Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們來還是不來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You coming or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah.
