Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得和他們取得聯系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have to talk to them.
