Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須得去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I gotta do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該留下來修好無線電  好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you should stay and fix the radio, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么修  發送器都砸碎了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fix it? The transmitter's smashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非有零件空降下來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unless there's a parts depot down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我們無法和方舟對話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we're not talking to the ark.
