Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:09:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道有個地方也許能給你弄到發送器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know a place you might be able to get a transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Great. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來你要和我一起來了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It looks like you're coming with me instead.
