Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也愛你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hello?
