Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱們需要繩子爬上來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need the rope to get back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手電筒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Flashlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要下到底下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm going all the way down.
