Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往那邊的印記更深一點\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The prints are deeper going that way.
