Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們帶走了她  那她還活著\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If they took her, she's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他們帶走我的時候一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like when they took me.
