Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想回去就回去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go back if you want. 
