Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是下地獄  我也要找到她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd walk into hell to find her.
