Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.40,0:39:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他帶到運輸船去  快點\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get him in the dropship now. Go!
